@using Condominium2000.Helpers
@using Condominium2000.Helpers.Models
@using Condominium2000.Resources
@using Condominium2000.Resources.Resident
@using Condominium2000.Resources.Shared
@model Condominium2000.Models.ViewModels.ResidentViewModel

@{
    ViewBag.Title = Index.VIEW_BAG_TITLE;
}

<link href="@Url.Content("~/Content/ImageSliderPromoted/js-image-slider-promoted.css")" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/>
<script src="@Url.Content("~/Scripts/ImageSliderPromoted/js-image-slider-promoted.js")" type="text/javascript"></script>

<div id="content_margin_top"></div>
<div id="content_center" class="center">
    <div id="content_top">
        <div id="content_margin_left"></div>
        <div id="content_small">
            <div id="sidebar_menu" class="sidebar_menu">
                @Html.Partial("_SubMenuPartial", ResidentHelper.SubMenu.GeneraInformation)
                <div class="sidebar_menu_divider"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="content_margin_middle"></div>
        <div id="content_large">
            <div id="default_info" class="default_info">
                <div class="sidebar_margin_xl"></div>
                @if (Request.IsAuthenticated)
                {
                    <div class="edit_link">
                        <p>
                            [@Html.ActionLink(EditLabels.LABEL_ADMIN_GALLERY_IMAGES, "AdminGalleryImages", new {controller = "GalleryImage"})]
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <br/>
                    <br/>
                }

                <div id="sliderFrame">
                    <div id="slider">
                        @foreach (var image in Model.FrontPageGalleryImages)
                        {
                            <img src="@image.FilePath" alt=""/>
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br/>
                <div class="sidebar_margin_xl"></div>
                @if (Request.IsAuthenticated)
                {
                    <div class="edit_link">
                        <p>
                            [@Html.ActionLink(EditLabels.LABEL_EDIT_RESIDENT_INFO, "EditResidentInfo", new {id = Model.ResidentTemplate.SelectedResidentInfo.Id})]
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <br/>
                }
                <div class="default_float_left">
                    <div class="default_html">
                        @Html.Raw(Html.ReturnLanguageContent(Model.ResidentTemplate.SelectedResidentInfo, TableContent.HtmlContent))
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="content_bottom" class="side_border">
        <div id="bottom_fast_links" class="quick_navigation">
            <div id="fl_divider">
                <div class="fl_divider"></div>
            </div>
            <div id="fl_space">
            </div>
            <div id="fl_news">
                @Html.ActionLinkBack(ContentBottom.BACK)
            </div>
            <div id="fl_top">
                @Html.ActionLinkTop(ContentBottom.TOP)
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>